{"type":"message","id":"7b670c74","parentId":"d83edeb9","timestamp":"2026-04-02T04:22:07.352Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"toolCall","id":"tooluse_ru1AubkjHEmSK20aAKFP83","name":"read","arguments":{"file":"/home/openclaw/.openclaw/workspace/memory/2026-04-01.md"}}],"api":"bedrock-converse-stream","provider":"amazon-bedrock","model":"us.anthropic.claude-opus-4-6-v1","usage":{"input":1,"output":71,"cacheRead":27522,"cacheWrite":811,"totalTokens":28405,"cost":{"input":0.000005,"output":0.001775,"cacheRead":0.013760999999999999,"cacheWrite":0.00506875,"total":0.02060975}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1775103724377}}
{"type":"message","id":"82319fbf","parentId":"7b670c74","timestamp":"2026-04-02T04:22:07.478Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"tooluse_ru1AubkjHEmSK20aAKFP83","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"# 2026-04-01 — Daily Notes\n\n## WhatsApp Gateway Flapping (04:14 UTC)\n- **Status:** WhatsApp gateway in 60-second disconnect/reconnect loop since ~00:34 UTC\n- **Root cause:** `creds.json` being flagged as corrupted every reconnect cycle → backup restore → reconnect → repeat\n- **Details:** 59 \"restored corrupted creds.json\" occurrences today. Status 499 (client-closed) every ~60s\n- **Investigation:** creds.json is actually valid JSON with correct fields (me.id, registrationId, etc.) — may be a file-locking/write-race issue\n- **Impact:** WhatsApp messages may work intermittently (brief connected windows), but loop wastes resources\n- **Gateway:** Running as openclaw-gateway (PID 1067470), child of openclaw supervisor (PID 1067463), NOT in PM2\n- **Action needed:** Lucy should try `openclaw gateway restart` or kill+restart the supervisor process when awake\n- **Risk:** Low — it's a nuisance loop, not data loss. Telegram still works fine.\n- **Note:** The gateway also reports whatsapp plugin as \"not found\" (stale config entry) — may need cleanup\n# 2026-04-01 — Daily Notes\n\n## WhatsApp Gateway Flapping (04:14 UTC)\n- **Status:** WhatsApp gateway in 60-second disconnect/reconnect loop since ~00:34 UTC\n- **Root cause:** `creds.json` being flagged as corrupted every reconnect cycle → backup restore → reconnect → repeat\n- **Details:** 59 \"restored corrupted creds.json\" occurrences today. Status 499 (client-closed) every ~60s\n- **Investigation:** creds.json is actually valid JSON with correct fields (me.id, registrationId, etc.) — may be a file-locking/write-race issue\n- **Impact:** WhatsApp messages may work intermittently (brief connected windows), but loop wastes resources\n- **Gateway:** Running as openclaw-gateway (PID 1067470), child of openclaw supervisor (PID 1067463), NOT in PM2\n- **Action needed:** Lucy should try `openclaw gateway restart` or kill+restart the supervisor process when awake\n- **Risk:** Low — it's a nuisance loop, not data loss. Telegram still works fine.\n- **Note:** The gateway also reports whatsapp plugin as \"not found\" (stale config entry) — may need cleanup\n\n## Sentra Brochure Copywriting Session (05:00-08:15 UTC)\n- **Context:** Lucy working on Sentra Technology product catalog/brosur in Canva\n- **My role:** Writing product descriptions, taglines, bullet points for each product page\n- **Products covered:**\n  1. **FMS (Fleet Management System)** — Dashboard, GPS tracking, ritase, BBM, CCTV, geofence, face recognition. Checked fms.sentratechnology.com demo vs brochure claims. 2/6 features fully present, 3 partial, 1 missing (CAN-Bus health).\n  2. **Custom Landing Page / Web App / Mobile App** — Combined into 1 package with 12 bullets + garansi & support 2 tahun\n  3. **HRIS** — Absensi GPS, face recognition, payroll, cuti, shift management\n  4. **Safety Attribute Detection (AI CCTV)** — APD detection (helm, safety belt, sepatu, rompi) + Starlink + Solar Panel\n  5. **Smart Lock System** — PIN, kartu, fingerprint, app access + monitoring\n  6. **SentrAI (On-Premise AI Server)** — 50 juta, server + AI + enkripsi\n  7. **Starlink Packages** (6 variants) — Home Starter, Home Basic, Home Ultra, Enterprise, Solar Coverage, Solar Coverage Max. Fixed all taglines (were all identical \"Cocok untuk penggunaan ringan & mobile\")\n  8. **Telematics (Teltonika)** — CAN-Bus, multi-sensor, dual-SIM, industrial grade, GPS, BBM monitoring, ADAS\n- **Key issue:** Space constraints in Canva — text kept overlapping. Had to shorten bullets multiple times.\n- **Format shift:** Lucy moved from multi-product-per-page to 1-product-per-page layout. Much cleaner.\n- **FMS page finalized** with 10 bullets + descriptive paragraph, price Rp 518 juta.\n- **Lucy asked if I can edit Canva directly** — told him it's not practical (UI-heavy), recommended sticking with copy-paste workflow.\n- **Sentra context:** This is Lucy's IT company (he's PM), separate from DataFlow. Products are for B2B sales in Kaltim.\n"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1775103727465}}
{"type":"message","id":"4717e289","parentId":"82319fbf","timestamp":"2026-04-02T04:22:10.183Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"toolCall","id":"tooluse_4H0UXJAWbjinc0Ua9ehyIp","name":"read","arguments":{"file":"/home/openclaw/.openclaw/workspace/memory/2026-03-31.md"}}],"api":"bedrock-converse-stream","provider":"amazon-bedrock","model":"us.anthropic.claude-opus-4-6-v1","usage":{"input":1,"output":71,"cacheRead":28333,"cacheWrite":1246,"totalTokens":29651,"cost":{"input":0.000005,"output":0.001775,"cacheRead":0.014166499999999999,"cacheWrite":0.0077875,"total":0.023733999999999998}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1775103727485}}
{"type":"message","id":"2f17b2e3","parentId":"4717e289","timestamp":"2026-04-02T04:22:10.228Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"tooluse_4H0UXJAWbjinc0Ua9ehyIp","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"# Memory — March 31, 2026\n\n## Major Build Day — Massive Feature Sprint\n\n### Sub-Agent Dispatch System (established today)\n- All 10+ agents now available for dispatch as sub-agents\n- Config updated: `subagents.allowAgents` includes all agents\n- Pattern: Lucy requests → Michael dispatches appropriate agent → agent runs autonomously → Michael relays results\n- Parallel dispatch works well (4 agents at once today)\n- **Lesson learned**: Don't manually fix things when I can dispatch Uriel. Lucy called this out.\n\n### MAGI v2 Features Built Today\n1. **WhatsApp Allowlist Manager** (Uriel) — Settings page, add/remove/label/role/access per contact\n2. **Message Forwarding Rules** (Uriel) — forward/forward_summarize/notify rules per contact\n3. **Personal Knowledge Base** (Rafael) — auto-save research, search, MAGI page at /magi2/knowledge/\n4. **Mini Roundtable** (Gabriel) — multi-agent discussion page at /magi2/roundtable/, 3 modes (on-demand, scheduled, smart trigger)\n5. **Smart Notifications** (Samael) — HEARTBEAT.md updated, cron setup docs, template responses\n6. **MAGI lama (/council) route removed** — using MAGI v2 (/magi2) only now\n\n### Paul Simulator (D&D Web App) — Full Build\n- Live at: https://64-227-110-70.sslip.io/dnd\n- Guide: https://64-227-110-70.sslip.io/dnd/guide.html\n- **Name**: \"Paul Simulator\" (not \"D&D 2024\", not \"Angkringan Balikpapan\")\n- **PIN-per-player auth**: DM gets 6-digit PIN, each player gets unique 4-digit PIN\n- **Features**: Character Sheet (2024 rules), 3D Dice Roller, Initiative Tracker, Spell Book, DM Party Overview, Session Notes, AI Summary, Save to Obsidian, NPC Manager + AI Generator, Monster Bestiary (50 monsters) + AI Generator, Combat Integration\n- **Known issues fixed**: RTL text reversal (use HTML dir=\"ltr\" not CSS), mobile layout overflow, dice auto-roll on select (should just select)\n- **Persistence**: localStorage for browser, JSON files server-side, auto-backup 7 days, Obsidian sync\n\n### Research Done (Metis)\n1. **Hitam Manis Cafe Balikpapan** — 10+ branches, 4.6/5, homegrown coffee chain\n2. **28 Coffee Balikpapan** — 22+ outlets nationwide, 4.7/5, owned by Platinum Hotel Group\n3. **D&D 2024 Rules Reference** — compiled manually after Metis timeout\n4. **NPC/Monster/Combat Mechanics** — research for Paul Simulator features\n\n### Contact Book Updates\n- **+6281345985715** = Ceka (NOT Kenny — gw salah awalnya)\n- **+6285161502503** = Kenny (keni)\n- **+6285159322166** = Paul (pavint2) — added to allowlist today\n- **Secret code for new contacts**: \"1+1 = ?\" → answer: \"Bahlil\" 😂\n\n### Kopilima Digital Core (SNC-K5) — NEW PROJECT\n- **Client**: Kopilima (Cafe chain, 10 cabang)\n- **Vendor**: Sentra (IT Software House) — Lucy is Manager at Sentra\n- **Lucy's real job**: Manager at Sentra software house (not just DataFlow founder)\n- **Project**: Custom POS + ERP system to replace Majoo\n- **Pillars**: K.I.S.S + Anti-Fraud Sovereignty\n- **Key modules**: Ghost Guard (anti-fraud), Midnight Protocol (inventory), QR Pre-Order, HCM/Payroll, Event Management, QR Membership\n- **Blueprint saved**: /knowledge-base/kopilima-snc-k5-blueprint.md\n- **Operational notes**: /knowledge-base/kopilima-operational-notes.md\n- **Michael's role**: Single Source of Truth, strategy guardian, meeting notes processor\n- Lucy meets Kopilima Direktur directly\n\n### Sentra WhatsApp Group\n- Lucy added gateway to \"g-notes-sentra\" group\n- Group detected but messages not triggering responses yet\n- Tag/mention not being detected — needs troubleshooting\n- Lucy wants me to respond in Sentra group (at least when tagged)\n\n### Cron Jobs Set Today\n- Kenny bubur ayam reminder (sent, but accidentally leaked to Paul's chat — lesson learned about session context)\n- 6 AM WITA + 7 AM WITA follow-up reminders for Kenny\n- Smart notification crons documented but NOT activated yet (waiting Lucy approval)\n\n### Lessons Learned\n- **Don't fix things manually when agents can do it** — Lucy called this out\n- **Session context matters** — reply went to wrong chat (Paul saw Kenny's bubur ayam reminder)\n- **RTL text bug**: Never use CSS `unicode-bidi: bidi-override` — use HTML `dir=\"ltr\"` attribute instead\n- **Sub-agent timeouts**: Large builds (like full app.js rewrite) timeout at 10min. Split into smaller tasks.\n- **Lucy prefers short answers** — still valid from previous memory\n- **Airdrop farming**: Lucy interested but needs burner wallet + X account access. Tabled for now.\n"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1775103730218}}
