{"type":"message","id":"d421e440","parentId":"20e4db14","timestamp":"2026-04-02T04:39:24.036Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"tooluse_3nroUCnrSO9a8spJ2LVREQ","toolName":"exec","content":[{"type":"text","text":"/home/openclaw/dnd-app/backend/server.js:1362:  const aiPrompt = `Generate a D&D 2024 player character. ${prompt}. Level: ${lvl}. ${classHint} ${speciesHint}${srdContext} Return ONLY valid JSON (no markdown, no explanation, no code fences) with these exact fields: {\"name\": string, \"species\": string (one of: Human, Elf, Dwarf, Halfling, Orc, Tiefling, Dragonborn, Gnome, Goliath, Aasimar), \"className\": string (one of: Barbarian, Bard, Cleric, Druid, Fighter, Monk, Paladin, Ranger, Rogue, Sorcerer, Warlock, Wizard), \"background\": string (one of: Acolyte, Artisan, Charlatan, Criminal, Entertainer, Farmer, Guard, Guide, Hermit, Merchant, Noble, Sage, Sailor, Scribe, Soldier, Wayfarer), \"level\": number, \"str\": number, \"dex\": number, \"con\": number, \"int\": number, \"wis\": number, \"cha\": number, \"hp\": number, \"maxHp\": number, \"ac\": number, \"speed\": number, \"alignment\": string, \"personalityTraits\": string, \"ideals\": string, \"bonds\": string, \"flaws\": string, \"backstory\": string, \"appearance\": string, \"equipment\": string, \"proficientSkills\": array of skill name strings (from: Acrobatics, Animal Handling, Arcana, Athletics, Deception, History, Insight, Intimidation, Investigation, Medicine, Nature, Perception, Performance, Persuasion, Religion, Sleight of Hand, Stealth, Survival), \"features\": array of {\"name\": string, \"desc\": string}}. Make ability scores realistic for the class. Make the character interesting and flavorful.`;"}],"details":{"status":"completed","exitCode":0,"durationMs":121,"aggregated":"/home/openclaw/dnd-app/backend/server.js:1362:  const aiPrompt = `Generate a D&D 2024 player character. ${prompt}. Level: ${lvl}. ${classHint} ${speciesHint}${srdContext} Return ONLY valid JSON (no markdown