{"type":"message","id":"c53c23ca","parentId":"efbb40cc","timestamp":"2026-04-02T04:40:31.624Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Now I understand the full picture. The feature `entries` are in English only. I need to:\n\n1. Fix `renderClassDetail` to translate labels (Proficiencies, Armor, etc.) when `isID`\n2. Improve `formatDesc` to properly format the text with bold sub-headings, bullet points, etc.\n3. For Indonesian translation of feature content — that's a massive data effort. But I can at least translate the UI labels and improve formatting.\n\nLet me also check how `t()` translation function works:"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"tooluse_sZNgYJmSTxSikGe7SohwWL","name":"read","arguments":{"file":"/home/openclaw/dnd-app/frontend/app.js","limit":40,"offset":8860}}],"api":"bedrock-converse-stream","provider":"amazon-bedrock","model":"us.anthropic.claude-opus-4-6-v1","usage":{"input":1,"output":221,"cacheRead":71022,"cacheWrite":531,"totalTokens":71775,"cost":{"input":0.000005,"output":0.005525,"cacheRead":0.035511,"cacheWrite":0.00331875,"total":0.04435975}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1775104824369}}
{"type":"message","id":"acee0ca0","parentId":"c53c23ca","timestamp":"2026-04-02T04:40:31.685Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"tooluse_sZNgYJmSTxSikGe7SohwWL","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"  let _lang = localStorage.getItem('dnd-compendium-lang') || 'id';\n  let _translations = null;\n  let _translationsLoaded = false;\n  let _displayedCount = 0;\n  let _currentData = [];\n\n  const ITEMS_PER_PAGE = 50;\n\n  // ---- i18n helpers ----\n  function t(key, fallback) {\n    if (_lang === 'en' || !_translations) return fallback || key;\n    return _translations.ui?.[key] || fallback || key;\n  }\n  function tDesc(category, index) {\n    if (_lang === 'en' || !_translations) return null;\n    const catMap = { 'races': 'species', 'items': 'equipment' };\n    const tCat = catMap[category] || category;\n    return _translations[tCat]?.[index] || null;\n  }\n  function tSchool(schoolName) {\n    if (_lang === 'en' || !_translations) return schoolName;\n    return _translations.ui?.[(schoolName || '').toLowerCase()] || schoolName;\n  }\n\n  async function loadTranslations() {\n    if (_translationsLoaded) return;\n    try {\n      _translations = await api('/srd/translations/id');\n      _translationsLoaded = true;\n    } catch (e) { console.warn('Failed to load translations:', e.message); }\n  }\n\n  function getLang() { return _lang; }\n  function toggleLang() {\n    _lang = _lang === 'id' ? 'en' : 'id';\n    localStorage.setItem('dnd-compendium-lang', _lang);\n    updateLangUI();\n    updateAllLabels();\n    fetchAndRender();\n  }\n\n[587 more lines in file. Use offset=8900 to continue.]"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1775104831671}}
{"type":"message","id":"30715b35","parentId":"acee0ca0","timestamp":"2026-04-02T04:40:44.701Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Now I have full context. The translation function `tDesc` maps class names to translated descriptions. But feature entries are all English. \n\nThe two things I can do now:\n1. **Translate UI labels** in `renderClassDetail` (Proficiencies → Profisiensi, etc.)\n2. **Fix formatting** — make `formatDesc` render sub-headings bold, add proper spacing, detect bullet points\n\nLet me fix both:"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"tooluse_gBnHHRzyAhhqg0fbAKZZJM","name":"edit","arguments":{"file":"/home/openclaw/dnd-app/frontend/app.js","oldText":"  function formatDesc(text) {\n    if (!text) return '';\n    return escapeHtml(text).replace(/\\n\\n/g, '</p><p>').replace(/\\n/g, '<br>');\n  }","newText":"  function formatDesc(text) {\n    if (!text) return '';\n    let html = escapeHtml(text);\n\n    // Detect known sub-heading patterns and bold them\n    // Lines that are short (< 40 chars), no period, followed by a newline + longer text\n    html = html.replace(/^([A-Z][A-Za-z '\\-]{2,38})$/gm, '<strong class=\"feature-subheading\">$1</strong>');\n\n    // Bullet points: lines starting with • or -\n    html = html.replace(/^[•\\-] (.+)$/gm, '<li>$1</li>');\n    // Wrap consecutive <li> in <ul>\n    html = html.replace(/((?:<li>.+<\\/li>\\n?)+)/g, '<ul class=\"feature-list\">$1</ul>');\n\n    // Double newlines = paragraph break\n    html = html.replace(/\\n\\n/g, '</p><p>');\n    // Single newline = line break (but not inside ul)\n    html = html.replace(/\\n/g, '<br>');\n\n    return html;\n  }"}}],"api":"bedrock-converse-stream","provider":"amazon-bedrock","model":"us.anthropic.claude-opus-4-6-v1","usage":{"input":1,"output":532,"cacheRead":71553,"cacheWrite":692,"totalTokens":72778,"cost":{"input":0.000005,"output":0.013300000000000001,"cacheRead":0.035776499999999996,"cacheWrite":0.004325,"total":0.0534065}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1775104831691}}
{"type":"message","id":"9c5d817e","parentId":"30715b35","timestamp":"2026-04-02T04:40:44.826Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"tooluse_gBnHHRzyAhhqg0fbAKZZJM","toolName":"edit","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Successfully replaced text in /home/openclaw/dnd-app/frontend/app.js."}],"details":{"diff":"      ...\n 9207   }\n 9208 \n 9209   function formatDesc(text) {\n 9210     if (!text) return '';\n-9211     return escapeHtml(text).replace(/\\n\\n/g, '</p><p>').replace(/\\n/g, '<br>');\n+9211     let html = escapeHtml(text);\n+9212 \n+9213     // Detect known sub-heading patterns and bold them\n+9214     // Lines that are short (< 40 chars), no period, followed by a newline + longer text\n+9215     html = html.replace(/^([A-Z][A-Za-z '\\-]{2,38})$/gm, '<strong class=\"feature-subheading\">$1</strong>');\n+9216 \n+9217     // Bullet points: lines starting with • or -\n+9218     html = html.replace(/^[•\\-] (.+)$/gm, '<li>$1</li>');\n+9219     // Wrap consecutive <li> in <ul>\n+9220     html = html.replace(/((?:<li>.+<\\/li>\\n?)+)/g, '<ul class=\"feature-list\">$1</ul>');\n+9221 \n+9222     // Double newlines = paragraph break\n+9223     html = html.replace(/\\n\\n/g, '</p><p>');\n+9224     // Single newline = line break (but not inside ul)\n+9225     html = html.replace(/\\n/g, '<br>');\n+9226 \n+9227     return html;\n 9212   }\n 9213 \n 9214   function renderSpellDetail(s) {\n 9215     const isID = _lang === 'id';\n      ...","firstChangedLine":9211},"isError":false,"timestamp":1775104844808}}
{"type":"message","id":"60ff2e7f","parentId":"9c5d817e","timestamp":"2026-04-02T04:40:59.785Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Now translate labels in `renderClassDetail`:"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"tooluse_pK2ruSvWld6hXZZrjN8Nsx","name":"edit","arguments":{"file":"/home/openclaw/dnd-app/frontend/app.js","newText":"    // Proficiencies section\n    let profHtml = `<div class=\"comp-detail-section\"><h3>${isID ? 'Profisiensi' : 'Proficiencies'}</h3>`;\n    if (c.profArmor?.length) profHtml += `<p><strong>${isID ? 'Armor' : 'Armor'}:</strong> ${escapeHtml(c.profArmor.join(', '))}</p>`;\n    if (c.profWeapons?.length) profHtml += `<p><strong>${isID ? 'Senjata' : 'Weapons'}:</strong> ${escapeHtml(c.profWeapons.join(', '))}</p>`;\n    if (c.profTools?.length) profHtml += `<p><strong>${isID ? 'Alat' : 'Tools'}:</strong> ${escapeHtml(c.profTools.join(', '))}</p>`;\n    if (c.profSaves?.length) profHtml += `<p><strong>Saving Throws:</strong> ${escapeHtml(c.profSaves.join(', '))}</p>`;\n    if (c.profSkills?.length) profHtml += `<p><strong>${isID ? 'Skill (pilih 2)' : 'Skills (choose 2)'}:</strong> ${escapeHtml(c.profSkills.join(', '))}</p>`;\n    profHtml += '</div>';\n\n    // Features by level\n    let featHtml = `<div class=\"comp-detail-section\"><h3>${isID ? 'Fitur per Level' : 'Features by Level'}</h3><div class=\"class-features-list\">`;\n    const features = c.features || [];\n    let currentLevel = -1;\n    features.forEach(f => {\n      if (f.level !== currentLevel) {\n        currentLevel = f.level;\n      }\n      featHtml += `\n        <div class=\"class-feature-item\">\n          <div class=\"feature-header\">\n            <span class=\"feature-name\">${escapeHtml(f.name)}</span>\n            <span class=\"feature-level\">Lvl ${f.level}</span>\n          </div>\n          <div class=\"feature-body\">${formatDesc(f.entries)}</div>\n        </div>`;\n    });\n    featHtml += '</div></div>';","oldText":"    // Proficiencies section\n    let profHtml = '<div class=\"comp-detail-section\"><h3>Proficiencies</h3>';\n    if (c.profArmor?.length) profHtml += `<p><strong>Armor:</strong> ${escapeHtml(c.profArmor.join(', '))}</p>`;\n    if (c.profWeapons?.length) profHtml += `<p><strong>Weapons:</strong> ${escapeHtml(c.profWeapons.join(', '))}</p>`;\n    if (c.profTools?.length) profHtml += `<p><strong>Tools:</strong> ${escapeHtml(c.profTools.join(', '))}</p>`;\n    if (c.profSaves?.length) profHtml += `<p><strong>Saving Throws:</strong> ${escapeHtml(c.profSaves.join(', '))}</p>`;\n    if (c.profSkills?.length) profHtml += `<p><strong>Skills (choose 2):</strong> ${escapeHtml(c.profSkills.join(', '))}</p>`;\n    profHtml += '</div>';\n\n    // Features by level\n    let featHtml = '<div class=\"comp-detail-section\"><h3>Features by Level</h3><div class=\"class-features-list\">';\n    const features = c.features || [];\n    let currentLevel = -1;\n    features.forEach(f => {\n      if (f.level !== currentLevel) {\n        currentLevel = f.level;\n      }\n      featHtml += `\n        <div class=\"class-feature-item\">\n          <div class=\"feature-header\">\n            <span class=\"feature-name\">${escapeHtml(f.name)}</span>\n            <span class=\"feature-level\">Lvl ${f.level}</span>\n          </div>\n          <div class=\"feature-body\">${formatDesc(f.entries)}</div>\n        </div>`;\n    });\n    featHtml += '</div></div>';"}}],"api":"bedrock-converse-stream","provider":"amazon-bedrock","model":"us.anthropic.claude-opus-4-6-v1","usage":{"input":1,"output":1208,"cacheRead":72245,"cacheWrite":563,"totalTokens":74017,"cost":{"input":0.000005,"output":0.0302,"cacheRead":0.0361225,"cacheWrite":0.00351875,"total":0.06984625000000001}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1775104844831}}
