{"type":"message","id":"482c34a7","parentId":"f91cfb13","timestamp":"2026-04-02T04:41:20.497Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"tooluse_QNPE5aEnkDk6BmCjuObsvQ","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":".class-feature-item {\n  border-left: 3px solid var(--gold-dim, #5c4c16);\n  padding: 8px 12px;\n  margin: 6px 0;\n  background: rgba(255,255,255,0.03);\n  border-radius: 0 var(--radius, 8px) var(--radius, 8px) 0;\n  cursor: pointer;\n  transition: background 0.2s, border-color 0.2s;\n}\n.class-feature-item:hover {\n  background: rgba(255,255,255,0.06);\n  border-left-color: var(--gold, #b8860b);\n}\n.class-feature-item .feature-header {\n  display: flex;\n  justify-content: space-between;\n  align-items: center;\n}\n.class-feature-item .feature-name {\n  font-weight: 600;\n  color: var(--text, #e0e0e0);\n}\n.class-feature-item .feature-level {\n  font-size: 0.8rem;\n  color: var(--gold, #b8860b);\n  font-weight: 700;\n  white-space: nowrap;\n}\n.class-feature-item .feature-body {\n  display: none;\n  margin-top: 8px;\n  font-size: 0.88rem;\n  color: var(--text-dim, #aaa);\n  line-height: 1.6;\n  white-space: pre-line;\n}\n.class-feature-item.expanded .feature-body {\n  display: block;\n}\n.subclass-group {\n  margin: 12px 0;\n  border: 1px solid var(--border, #333);\n  border-radius: var(--radius, 8px);\n  overflow: hidden;\n}\n.subclass-group-header {\n  background: rgba(var(--gold-rgb, 184,134,11), 0.1);\n  padding: 10px 14px;\n  cursor: pointer;\n  display: flex;\n\n[129 more lines in file. Use offset=5970 to continue.]"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1775104880483}}
{"type":"message","id":"c4a568d8","parentId":"482c34a7","timestamp":"2026-04-02T04:41:28.967Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"I see! The feature bodies are `display: none` by default and shown on click (expanded class). So the wall-of-text issue is about formatting *within* the expanded body. Let me add CSS for the new formatting elements:"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"tooluse_WAMfz82n0bY8mKyv5bxLG7","name":"edit","arguments":{"file":"/home/openclaw/dnd-app/frontend/styles.css","newText":".class-feature-item .feature-body {\n  display: none;\n  margin-top: 8px;\n  font-size: 0.88rem;\n  color: var(--text-dim, #aaa);\n  line-height: 1.6;\n  white-space: normal;\n}\n.class-feature-item .feature-body .feature-subheading {\n  display: block;\n  color: var(--gold, #b8860b);\n  font-size: 0.9rem;\n  margin-top: 0.6rem;\n  margin-bottom: 0.2rem;\n}\n.class-feature-item .feature-body .feature-list {\n  list-style: disc;\n  padding-left: 1.2rem;\n  margin: 0.4rem 0;\n}\n.class-feature-item .feature-body .feature-list li {\n  margin-bottom: 0.2rem;\n}\n.class-feature-item .feature-body p {\n  margin: 0.4rem 0;\n}","oldText":".class-feature-item .feature-body {\n  display: none;\n  margin-top: 8px;\n  font-size: 0.88rem;\n  color: var(--text-dim, #aaa);\n  line-height: 1.6;\n  white-space: pre-line;\n}"}}],"api":"bedrock-converse-stream","provider":"amazon-bedrock","model":"us.anthropic.claude-opus-4-6-v1","usage":{"input":1,"output":486,"cacheRead":74880,"cacheWrite":653,"totalTokens":76020,"cost":{"input":0.000005,"output":0.012150000000000001,"cacheRead":0.03744,"cacheWrite":0.00408125,"total":0.05367625}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1775104880506}}
