{"type":"message","id":"29007d87","parentId":"742b115d","timestamp":"2026-04-02T04:41:36.448Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Wait — I also see that the screenshot shows features are expanded by default (not collapsed). Let me look at the screenshot again — it's the full modal content displayed as one long page. The feature body is showing as one massive wall of text. The issue is `white-space: pre-line` was preserving newlines but not adding structure. My CSS change to `white-space: normal` + the formatDesc improvements should fix that.\n\nBut looking at the screenshot more carefully, the features seem to NOT be in the collapsible pattern — they're all expanded. Let me check if there's a different render path for the modal:"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"tooluse_JWY1FfAFW7BbVn7CrSv3UU","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"grep -n \"comp-detail-overlay\\|detail-overlay\\|showDetail\\|renderDetail\" /home/openclaw/dnd-app/frontend/app.js | head -15"}}],"api":"bedrock-converse-stream","provider":"amazon-bedrock","model":"us.anthropic.claude-opus-4-6-v1","usage":{"input":1,"output":227,"cacheRead":75533,"cacheWrite":518,"totalTokens":76279,"cost":{"input":0.000005,"output":0.005675,"cacheRead":0.0377665,"cacheWrite":0.0032375000000000004,"total":0.046683999999999996}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1775104889038}}
{"type":"message","id":"9979321e","parentId":"29007d87","timestamp":"2026-04-02T04:41:36.526Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"tooluse_JWY1FfAFW7BbVn7CrSv3UU","toolName":"exec","content":[{"type":"text","text":"9093:    card.addEventListener('click', () => showDetail(category, item));\n9176:  function showDetail(category, item) {\n9177:    const overlay = $('#compendium-detail-overlay');\n9436:      $('#compendium-detail-overlay')?.classList.add('hidden');\n9438:    $('#compendium-detail-overlay')?.addEventListener('click', (e) => {\n9442:      if (e.key === 'Escape') $('#compendium-detail-overlay')?.classList.add('hidden');"}],"details":{"status":"completed","exitCode":0,"durationMs":45,"aggregated":"9093:    card.addEventListener('click', () => showDetail(category, item));\n9176:  function showDetail(category, item) {\n9177:    const overlay = $('#compendium-detail-overlay');\n9436:      $('#compendium-detail-overlay')?.classList.add('hidden');\n9438:    $('#compendium-detail-overlay')?.addEventListener('click', (e) => {\n9442:      if (e.key === 'Escape') $('#compendium-detail-overlay')?.classList.add('hidden');","cwd":"/home/openclaw/.openclaw/workspace"},"isError":false,"timestamp":1775104896513}}
{"type":"message","id":"fd1c1fae","parentId":"9979321e","timestamp":"2026-04-02T04:41:39.998Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"toolCall","id":"tooluse_Qi5s6jhO4iQ5pjhb8sDKny","name":"read","arguments":{"file":"/home/openclaw/dnd-app/frontend/app.js","limit":40,"offset":9176}}],"api":"bedrock-converse-stream","provider":"amazon-bedrock","model":"us.anthropic.claude-opus-4-6-v1","usage":{"input":1,"output":101,"cacheRead":76051,"cacheWrite":366,"totalTokens":76519,"cost":{"input":0.000005,"output":0.0025250000000000003,"cacheRead":0.0380255,"cacheWrite":0.0022875,"total":0.04284299999999999}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1775104896533}}
{"type":"message","id":"d3abaa53","parentId":"fd1c1fae","timestamp":"2026-04-02T04:41:40.050Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"tooluse_Qi5s6jhO4iQ5pjhb8sDKny","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"  function showDetail(category, item) {\n    const overlay = $('#compendium-detail-overlay');\n    const content = $('#compendium-detail-content');\n    if (!overlay || !content) return;\n\n    let html = '';\n    if (category === 'spells') html = renderSpellDetail(item);\n    else if (category === 'classes') html = renderClassDetail(item);\n    else if (category === 'races') html = renderRaceDetail(item);\n    else if (category === 'items') html = renderItemDetail(item);\n    else if (category === 'feats') html = renderFeatDetail(item);\n    else if (category === 'backgrounds') html = renderBackgroundDetail(item);\n    else if (category === 'conditions') html = renderConditionDetail(item);\n    else html = renderGenericDetail(item);\n\n    content.innerHTML = html;\n\n    // Wire up collapsible features\n    content.querySelectorAll('.class-feature-item').forEach(el => {\n      el.addEventListener('click', () => el.classList.toggle('expanded'));\n    });\n    content.querySelectorAll('.subclass-group-header').forEach(el => {\n      el.addEventListener('click', () => el.parentElement.classList.toggle('expanded'));\n    });\n\n    overlay.classList.remove('hidden');\n  }\n\n  function mod(score) {\n    const m = Math.floor(((score || 10) - 10) / 2);\n    return m >= 0 ? `+${m}` : `${m}`;\n  }\n\n  function formatDesc(text) {\n    if (!text) return '';\n    let html = escapeHtml(text);\n\n    // Detect known sub-heading patterns and bold them\n    // Lines that are short (< 40 chars), no period, followed by a newline + longer text\n    html = html.replace(/^([A-Z][A-Za-z '\\-]{2,38})$/gm, '<strong class=\"feature-subheading\">$1</strong>');\n\n[287 more lines in file. Use offset=9216 to continue.]"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1775104900040}}
